---
name: Web Search Minimal Test
description: Minimal prompt to instruct LLM to use native web_search and report results
version: 1.0.0

inputs:
  query:
    description: Search query string
    type: string
    default: "Yoco company overview"

model:
  api: responses
  configuration:
    connection: openai_conn
    model: gpt-5-mini
    type: openai_chat
    tools: [web_search]
  # Request native tool result payloads for deterministic validation
  parameters:
    max_tokens: 200
    include:
      - "web_search_call.results"

processing_config:
  source_collection: Domain

---

system:
You are a test assistant. Your only job is to use the native web_search tool to fetch real-time results.

CRITICAL REQUIREMENTS:
- ALWAYS call web_search for this task (do not answer from memory)
- Use the exact query value provided
- After calling web_search, list the top 3 results with Title and URL
- If no results are returned, output the string: "No results"

user:
Execute web_search for "{{ query }}" and summarize the top 3 results.
